---
import { personal } from "../data/content";
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-light tracking-tight text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-6">About</h2>
  <div class="max-w-2xl text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
    <p>
      I'm a data analyst and analytics engineer based in the {personal.location} with
      experience spanning fintech, healthcare, and retail. I specialize in turning complex,
      messy data into clear decisions — whether that's building scalable dbt projects,
      creating BI dashboards, or running statistical analysis.
    </p>
    <p>
      I hold an Advanced dbt Certification from Uplimit, a Certificate in Data Science and
      Data Analytics from UCSC Extension, and a Master of Arts in Economics and Geography
      from the University of Aberdeen.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
